column5: Dont know too much about Virginia Beach parking, but there is limited parking at Port Bolster.  There a variety store there and a guy charges $10 to park, but you have to get there early.  I just head to gilford now cause I dont want to get there and theres nothing available.
Be sure to tell us how high the ice stack is over there!!
Don't want to be on Guilford yet with 4 of us in the hut. Reports have been showing better ice in VB and PB
Im heading out to Gilford on Wednesday so good luck to you.  Time to catch some jumbos
I'll be heading out from VB tomorrow morning.  Rich.
Im heading to gilford in the morning,Just checking the weather now, i hate to leave the quad at home but next week it will be safer for the quad.
